Matter Server container image preload for Saha images.

Build-time source priority:

1. ${DL_DIR}/matter-server-container.tar
2. Host Docker image tagged ghcr.io/matter-js/python-matter-server:arm64
3. Host Docker image ghcr.io/matter-js/python-matter-server:stable (retagged to arm64)
4. Remote registry fetch of ghcr.io/matter-js/python-matter-server:stable with skopeo

At runtime the launcher loads the archive and ensures the image is available as
ghcr.io/matter-js/python-matter-server:arm64.
